0.4.0-l1n-1 (2018-04-19)
    - don't output empty required arrays
    - don't export any required fields for `partial=True` schemas
    - make nested schemas instantiate from the same class as the current one to
      support subclassing

0.4.0 (2017-07-13)
    - add support for fields.List (thanks @Bartvds and @sdayu
      for tests & implementation)

0.3.0 (2016-06-12)
    - add support for marshmallow validators (see #14)

0.2.0 (2016-05-25)
    - add support for titles & descriptions in metadata
